questions.quote: I can't believe her! Did she tell you we were having money problems?
He even offered to meet me for lunch tomorrow to prep me for it.
Ross, just forget about it. This guy's got you totally wedged in.
Yeah, I-I-I just pulled the tab and I just fogged his yeti ass!
You don't understand! Elizabeth was about to ask me to go on a trip with her! Is that taking it slow?! No, I'm not ready for this! Okay? What-what do I tell her?
Everybody smile! Okay, thanks a lot! Enjoy your stay at Caesar's! We hope it's toga-rrific! Kill me. Kill me now.
But you-you said black. Why would he want his blue blazer black?
Look Rach, wasn't this supposed to a temporary thing? I thought you wanted to do fashion stuff?
No, it's not a divorce, it is not a divorce! Anyway, I think Rachel and I need to, you know, get on with our lives, maybe, maybe start seeing other people.
Yeah, but Janice? That-that was like the worst breakup in history!
